==English==

===Etymology===
From the [[hypothetical]] [[planet]] Vulcan, erroneously believed to exist within the orbit of Mercury

===Noun===
'''Vulcanoid'''

# {{astronomy}} An [[asteroid]] that orbits in a [[dynamically]] stable zone between 0.08 and 0.21 [[AU]] from the Sun

===Adjective===
'''Vulcanoid'''

# {{astronomy}} Of or dealing with a Vulcanoid

